item.title: Need help with joining Hamachi servers please
item.dc:creator: @m0nsterb0ys m0nsterb0ys
item.description:
@m0nsterb0ys wrote:

quint_nl:

I downloaded Hamachi now and when i give the pass and name the port and the ip I still cant join servers… at hamachi i see a whole list of servers wut do i need to do there?[br][size=1]Posted on: May 05, 2007, 05:55:49 AM[/size][hr]bump help me

U got hamachi?

ok first find out the server network and network pass.(open the hamachi menu thing with the server list) then click on the triangle on the bottom right hand corner by the hamachi config button. Click Join a new exsisting network. enter the network name and pass there. Once that is done open moparisthebest.com and put in your name and pass and ip. make sure u have the right ip and if u need a different port then default (43594) then go on the top menu bar, on the left click file:new port: then enter the port you need. Hope this helps

Ps. If it still says error connecting to serve, then the server must be down
